<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>A Canadian author and investigative journalist claims to have ‘new testimony from a bevy of women’ who allege they have been 'intimate with The Duke of York'. </p>

<p>Ian Halperin is set to publish a series of books, 'Sex Lies and Dirty Money By The World's Powerful Elite' later this month. </p>

<p>He claims the book will provide new information on Prince Andrew's relationship with Jeffrey Epstein. </p>

<p>A Canadian author is claiming to have the inside story on Prince Andrew's relationship with paedophile billionaire financier Jeffrey Epstein </p>

<p>Epstein killed himself in prison while awaiting charges on sex trafficking </p>

<p>The author has listed the book on Amazon, which he claims will make 'world headlines'. </p>

<p>According to The Sun, Halperin said: 'It's going to shed a lot of light.</p>

<p>'l'll say one thing after my book, if Prince Andrew is not finally interrogated by the Feds, we've got a major problem because I'm unleashing a ton (of) never before revealed stuff.</p>

<p>'About the Epstein case, about Maxwell, especially about Prince Andrew and about a plethora of other people connected to Epstein whose roles have never been revealed before.'</p>

<p>The Prince Andrew story is part of a six-volume book and later editions will concentrate on issues surrounding Prince Harry and Meghan Markle and Megxit.  </p>

<p>Prince Andrew has continually denied all allegations of impropriety concerning his dealings with paedophile billionaire Jeffrey Epstein which have forced his stepping back from public life.</p>
